ActMeat Inspection Act
PrecisRegulations Amending the MEAT INSPECTION REGULATIONS, 1990 by clarifying that all meat products, including whole carcasses and primal cuts, produced in a federal penitentiary and shipped to another one in a different province, are exempt from certain requirements of the Act.
